ActPayments in Lieu of Taxes Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHEL DOYON, Q.C., of Ste-Foy, Quebec, to be a member of the Payments in Lieu of Taxes Dispute Advisory Panel to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and appointment of MICHEL DOYON, Q.C., a member of the advisory panel, as Chairperson of the Payments in Lieu of Taxes Dispute Advisory Panel.
